schemaVersion: 1
id: music-factory-root
name: Music Factory
kind: root
version: 0.1.0
description: >
  Compose songs in Python, render them as MIDI, and play them in the browser
  with a live note-by-note visualizer. Includes the Portal song "Still Alive"
  as a full-screen Cabinet app, NSync's "Bye Bye Bye" as a Python script that
  emits a MIDI file, and a how-to guide for writing your own song from
  scratch with mido + pygame.
entry: index.md
